00:54:16.045 --> 00:54:17.420
XIAOXING XI: As
a matter of fact,

00:54:17.420 --> 00:54:21.790
there are organizations
like the Coalition

00:54:21.790 --> 00:54:25.780
to End the National
Security Scapegoating,

00:54:25.780 --> 00:54:32.920
