rights organizations

00:54:35.530 --> 00:54:39.280
from other minority groups.

00:54:39.280 --> 00:54:45.550
I think what people can do is
to at least pay attention to it.

00:54:45.550 --> 00:54:51.655
Probably go to
the event and then

00:54:51.655 --> 00:54:55.550
